OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fcloudy and breezy overnight, with
OL,7,Ffurther outbreaks of rain and fog over
OL,8,Fthe Derbyshire hills. Heavier and more
OL,9,Fpersistent rain spreads northeast
OL,10,Fafter midnight before clearing to just
OL,11,Fthe odd shower before dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FCloudy with most parts dry,
OL,14,Fbut also a few showers, perhaps heavy.
OL,15,FWarm in any brighter spells that
OL,16,Fdevelop. Heavy rain and gusty winds
OL,17,Fthen move east late afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
